<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🎉 You Won in the HonestNeed Sweepstakes!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .header-emoji {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .prize-box {
            background-color: #fcd34d;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .prize-amount {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #d97706;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .prize-details {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        .detail-value {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111827;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .deadline-warning {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #991b1b;
        }
        .section {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .section-content {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .stat {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-top: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .center-text {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-emoji">🎉</div>
            <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">You Won in the HonestNeed Sweepstakes!</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hi <%= firstName %>,
            </div>

            <p>
                We're thrilled to announce that you've been selected as a winner in our <%= period %> HonestNeed sweepstakes drawing! 🏆
            </p>

            <!-- Prize Box -->
            <div class="prize-box">
                <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #b45309; margin-bottom: 10px;">Your Prize Amount</div>
                <div class="prize-amount">$<%= prizeAmount %></div>
                <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #b45309;">This will be added to your HonestNeed wallet</div>
            </div>

            <!-- How You Won -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">🎯 How You Won</div>
                <div class="stats">
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= entryCount %></div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Entries</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="stat-value"><%= probability %>%</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Probability</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    You accumulated <%= entryCount %> sweepstakes entries through shares, donations, and other HonestNeed activities. With <%= totalParticipants %> participants in this drawing, you had a <%= probability %>% chance of winning. Congratulations on your luck! 🍀
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Claim Instructions -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">📝 How to Claim Your Prize</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <ol style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Click the button below to visit your winnings page</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Select your preferred payment method</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Click "Claim Prize"</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 0;">The funds will appear in your HonestNeed wallet within 24 hours</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
                <div class="center-text">
                    <a href="<%= claimUrl %>" class="cta-button">Claim Your Prize</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Deadline Warning -->
            <div class="deadline-warning">
                <strong>⚠️ Important Deadline:</strong> You must claim your prize by <strong><%= claimDeadline %></strong>. After this date, the prize may be forfeited.
            </div>

            <!-- Prize Details -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">💰 Prize Details</div>
                <div class="prize-details">
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <span class="detail-label">Prize Amount:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">$<%= prizeAmount %></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <span class="detail-label">Drawing Period:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value"><%= period %></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <span class="detail-label">Claim Deadline:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value"><%= claimDeadline %></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-row">
                        <span class="detail-label">Payment Method:</span>
                        <span class="detail-value">Your Choice</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">❓ Frequently Asked Questions</div>
                <div class="section-content">
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        <strong>Can I withdraw this prize?</strong><br>
                        Yes! Once claimed, the prize money appears in your HonestNeed wallet and can be withdrawn to your bank account anytime.
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                        <strong>How are winners selected?</strong><br>
                        Winners are selected using a provably fair algorithm (Vose's Alias Method) that gives every entry an equal chance based on the number of entries they have.
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>What if I don't claim my prize?</strong><br>
                        If you don't claim your prize by the deadline, it will be forfeit. Make sure to claim it before <%= claimDeadline %>!
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Closing -->
            <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                <p>
                    Thank you for participating in HonestNeed and supporting campaigns! Your engagement—through sharing, donating, and creating campaigns—directly fuels our community impact. 🌱
                </p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                    Keep sharing, keep supporting, and good luck in next month's drawing!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">
                <strong>HonestNeed</strong> | The Giving Platform
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0;">
                Questions? <a href="mailto:support@honestneed.org">Contact Support</a> | 
                <a href="https://honestneed.org/sweepstakes">Learn More About Sweepstakes</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #9ca3af;">
                © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> HonestNeed. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
